   <!-- Section 1 -->
   <section class="about-section">
     <h2>Why Carrier Shark Exists</h2>
     <p>
       Freight brokers operate in an environment where carrier authority status,
       insurance validity, documentation, and agreements directly impact risk exposure.
       Yet most workflows rely on scattered spreadsheets, inbox searches, or manual tracking.
     </p>
     <p>
       Carrier Shark centralizes carrier visibility into a single system designed
       specifically for brokers — not compliance checklists, not onboarding gimmicks,
       and not generic document storage.
     </p>
